org.dataconservancy.packaging.tool.model

Class OpenedPackage

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.dataconservancy.packaging.tool.model.OpenedPackage

  • public class OpenedPackage
extends Object
    Represents a serialized package which has been extracted to a location on the file system. The package state is returned unmodified from the opened package. The tree stored in this object has been modified from the package state so that it references files extracted to the base directory.
